- create new branch

    git branch mybranch

- switch to branch

    git checkout mybranch

- create and switch in one go

    git checkout -b mybranch

- list branches

    git branch

- delete branches

    git branch -d mybranch stablebranch newbranch

- merging branch

    # go to the more ancient branch
    git checkout oldbranch

    # pull in changes from "newbranch", it will fast-forward 
    # "oldbranch's" pointer to commit pointed at by "newbranch"
    git merge newbranch

- last commit on each branch

    git branch -v 

- filtering out merged or unmerged

    git branch --merge --no-merged

    
